*Straha* je bila toliko velika da se nisam usuđivala da krenem. (Fear was so great that I didn't dare to start.)

Kad je čuo prvi udarac, njegova *straha* je postala još veća. (When he heard the first blow, his fear became even greater.)

Kako je rasla *straha*, počeo je da se znoji po čelu. (As the fear grew, he began to sweat on his forehead.)

Ona je osetila *strahu* i počela da se udaljava. (She felt fear and began to move away.)

*Strahovi* su mu stalno prisutni u svakodnevnom životu. (Fears are constantly present in his everyday life.)